@d1 1
a1 1
.\"	$OpenBSD$
a38 10
.Pp
Each of the host's network addresses is specified at boot time with a
.Dv SIOCSIFADDR
.Xr ioctl 2 .
The
.Nm
interface employs the address resolution protocol described in
.Xr arp 4
to dynamically map between Internet and Ethernet addresses on the
local network.
@

